  "key_feedforward": "after init permute and before final permute: S[4+i] ^= K[i]; tag words: T_i = S[i] ^ K[i] for i in 0..1",
  "padding": "pad10star: 0x01 marker always present; a positive block-aligned AAD/message length emits one extra all-padding block (marker in rate byte 0); empty fields skipped. Length bits of AAD and MSG XORed into S[4],S[5] before final key feedforward.",
